WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:01.710
To create an assignment in the module,

1
00:00:01.929 --> 00:00:03.880
click the plus button under the header.

2
00:00:04.289 --> 00:00:04.690
From there,

3
00:00:04.760 --> 00:00:07.469
select the create button and then select document.

4
00:00:07.929 --> 00:00:08.850
In the document menu,

5
00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.729
click the upload button and select the file to be used.

6
00:00:12.380 --> 00:00:14.460
There are 3 viewing options for files,

7
00:00:14.939 --> 00:00:15.859
view only,

8
00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:17.610
view and download,

9
00:00:17.940 --> 00:00:18.940
and download only.

10
00:00:20.170 --> 00:00:22.040
Select the option that works best.

11
00:00:22.780 --> 00:00:26.260
Then create a name for the file that is easily understood by students.

12
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:27.829
From there,

13
00:00:28.159 --> 00:00:29.819
change the availability to

14
00:00:29.959 --> 00:00:32.380
visible to students and click save.